                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="Inliner" style="width:310px">
                        <div class="DesignBodyText" style="width:310px">
                             <h2 class="Squished">WE ARE THE  <span style="color: red">OFFICIAL</span> AND <span style="color: red">EXCLUSIVE DISTRIBUTOR</span> OF PROTAL, A HIGHLY 
                                DURABLE, FIRE RETARDANT FABRIC.
                           <br /><br />
